node.text:
An action-packed day of topwater fishing has never been easier than when you tie on the Shimano Coltsniper Splash Walk. Hop in the boat with Capt. Jack @east_coast_charters as he breaks down lure color options, advantages of fishing the Splash Walk and best practices to ignite deafening explosions from giant striped bass this season.

Learn more about the Coltsniper Splash Walk and communicate with your local dealers about availability today by heading to our link in bio.

#FishShimano #ShimanoColtsniper #ColtsniperSplashWalk

node.text:
Constructed on a high-modulus graphite blank, Clarus rods feature a Shimano Custom Reel Seat as well Titanium Oxide guides to minimize friction and increase line flow for maximum casting distance and durability when fishing with light braided fishing line.

Do you have a Shimano Clarus rod in your inshore lineup?

#FishShimano #ShimanoClarus #Clarus

node.text:
Shimano designed the Coltsniper Walk Hi-Pitch with a glass fiber construction that emits a high-pitch rattling sound when working across the surface. This enticing "walk the dog" style topwater is guaranteed to produce picture-perfect moments on the water.

#FishShimano #ColtsniperWalk #ShimanoColtsniper

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 18, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod, indoor and body of water.

node.text:
The new and noteworthy Shimano Sustain.

Since its announcement at ICAST last month, there have been nothing but rave reviews about the new Sustain. The Shimano Sustain is built with the power and rigidity to handle any angling scenario - from freshwater bass to bull redfish.

#FishShimano #ShimanoSustain #Sustain

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing in Gulf Of Mexico with @captmojeaux421, @journeysouthoutfitters, and @jpderoseoutdoors. May be an image of one or more people, people fishing, people standing, fishing rod, body of water and text that says 'SHIMANO SCHOOL OFFSHORE OIL RIGS CaPT. moe NEWMAN OF JOURNEY SOUTH OUTFITTERS AUGUST 17, 2021 8PM EST'.

node.text:
Join us TONIGHT when @jpderoseoutdoors is joined by @captmojeaux421 of @journeysouthoutfitters - accredited inshore/offshore captain in the Gulf of Mexico (and owner of the amazing boat pups from our last post)! 

The two will chat about the incredible fishery that exists around the abundant Gulf of Mexico Oil Rigs and the best tactics to fish these structures!

Get your questions ready as Moe targets a massive amount of species with a myriad of techniques. 

Tag a friend who still has a day of Gulf oil rig fishing on their bucket list below! 

You can tune for free via the Shimano Facebook or YouTube. Head to our link in bio to set a reminder!

We’ll see you at 8PM EST. 👊

#FishShimano #CloserToNature #ShimanoSchool

node.text:
A long scouting session in the dog days of summer will leave you feeling pretty exhausted...

#FishShimano #OffshoreFishing #DogsWhoFish
📽️: @journeysouthoutfitters

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 15, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and body of water.

node.text:
Designed to impart proper action on various styles of jigs, slow jigging rods load more parabolically than conventional jigging rods to give the angler greater control over the movement of the jig. Shimano designed the new Game Type Slow J rods to fish with lighter @powerpro braid and leader to ensure a fluid connection between rod movements and the jig. 

What's your ideal depth for deploying vertical jigs?

#FishShimano #GameTypeSlowJ #JiggingRods #ShimanoRods

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 14, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod, body of water and text that says 'NASCI'.

node.text:
The new Nasci series of spinning reels answers the call for anglers demanding smoothness and durability in multiple fishing applications. Suitable in both freshwater and inshore saltwater environments, the new Nasci reels feature CoreProtect to increase durability and water resistance without creating an additional heavy rotational feeling. 

#FishShimano #ShimanoNasci #Nasci

node.text:

#FishShimano #BassFishing #SightFishing
📸: jkinner_fishing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 12, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and body of water.

node.text:
The Shimano Stella SW is a true saltwater icon with the pulling power to stop a leviathan in its tracks. This legendary reel lineup features max drag ratings up to 62 pounds and a Heatsink Drag system that gives anglers the confidence to push it to the max.

#FishShimano #ShimanoStella #StellaSW

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 11, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and body of water.

node.text:
Improving upon the standard protection against corrosion, the Shimano Ultegra FC incorporates Shimano's X-Protect technology - a specially designed, water channeling, labyrinth construction -making it the ideal weapon for soldiers who operate on saltwater battlefields.

Which setup would you draw first: red or blue?

#FishShimano #ShimanoUltegra #UltegraFC
